[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Construction cost]]


Sets the cost of construction in the game.<br><br>
0 = low<br>
1 = medium<br>
2 = high<br>

<pre>
[difficulty]
construction_cost = 0
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 | 2 ]

'''Default:''' 1


